channel.title: [bug]ALLSTAR WEBCLIENT[/bug]
channel.description:
So as you can see in [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,517106.0.html]This Post[/url],I found out that this part was messed up
I used to have this, in my client.java [code=java]downloadcache("http://neroscape.com/neroscape_cache.zip", "cache.zip", "", "cache"); [/code]
Then I fixed it to this [code=java]downloadcache("http://neroscape.com/neroscape_cache.zip", "neroscape_cache.zip", "", "cache"); [/code]
**NOTE** I changed the second cache.zip to neroscape_cache.zip
And now, it downloads the cache EXTREMELY fast, but it doesn't show it in my C:\ directory...
And once it's done downloading the cache it gives me this error [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/ekndhz.jpg[/img]
Any Idea of what's wrong?:\
You can test for yourself by [url=http://www.neroscape.com/webclient.php]Clicking Here[/url]
I am not advertising! If anybody has any problems with this post I will edit it back to MYCLIENT...
BUMP
Sincerely, FILLOST
